    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the playing of AI generated music in shops and commercial premises",
        "additional_details": "AI music is jarring to listen to for staff and customers and damages creativity.\r\n\r\nI understand why many premises do not want to pay the music licence but I think they should play old music that is out of copyright or not play music at all.",
        "background": "Ban the playing of music generated entirely by AI in shops, restaurants, offices etc.",
